Package: egrandis
Type: Package
Title: Growth and Yield Models for Eucalyptus grandis Clonal Plantations
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("tsuga0722",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(GITHUB = "tsuga0722"))
  )
Description: Simulates growth, mortality, thinning response, and yield in
    Eucalyptus grandis plantations across a range of management regimes,
    intended for operational forestry planning in subtropical regions.
    Currently provides a faithful reproduction of the INIA SAG grandis 2021
    system (Rachid-Casnati et al. 2019; Methol 2003) validated against the
    online simulator at sag.inia.uy. A second simulator with augmented
    site-variable predictors and density-driven self-thinning, intended for
    local PSP-data calibration, is in development.
